{
  "page": "Home",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> While partially based on material from the fourth and fifth novels, <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> respectively, <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">Season 6</a> of the television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i> is also based on material from the unreleased sixth novel <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>. Therefore, this page might contain spoilers for the sixth book.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(248, 233, 208);border:none;\">\"Home\"</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size: 100%\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:right;\">Season 6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">&#160;—&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:left;\">Episode 2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original air date</th><td>\nMay 1, 2016</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Running time</th><td>\n54 minutes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Credits</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Directed by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Podeswa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jeremy Podeswa\">Jeremy Podeswa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dave_Hill_(screenwriter)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dave Hill (screenwriter)\">Dave Hill</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Episode chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">←&#160;Previous</th>\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">Next&#160;→</th>\n</tr><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Red_Woman\" title=\"The Red Woman\">The Red Woman</a>\"</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/Oathbreaker\" title=\"Oathbreaker\">Oathbreaker</a>\"</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/List_of_Game_of_Thrones_episodes\" title=\"List of Game of Thrones episodes\">List of episodes</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>\"<b>Home</b>\" is the second episode of the <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">sixth season</a> of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HBO\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:HBO\">HBO</a>'s <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medieval_fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Medieval fantasy\">medieval fantasy</a> television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>. It is the fifty-second episode of the series overall. Running 54 minutes long, it first aired on May 1, 2016. The episode was written by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dave_Hill_(screenwriter)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dave Hill (screenwriter)\">Dave Hill</a>, and directed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeremy_Podeswa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jeremy Podeswa\">Jeremy Podeswa</a>. Music was composed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramin_Djawadi\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ramin Djawadi\">Ramin Djawadi</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Official_synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Official synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Cast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cast</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Starring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Starring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Co-starring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Co-starring</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Official_synopsis\">Official synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Home&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Official synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Bran goes home. The Night's Watch stands behind Thorne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cast\">Cast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Home&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Cast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Starring\">Starring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Home&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Starring\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Dinklage\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Peter Dinklage\">Peter Dinklage</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nikolaj_Coster-Waldau\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nikolaj Coster-Waldau\">Nikolaj Coster-Waldau</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lena_Headey\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Lena Headey\">Lena Headey</a> as Queen Mother <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kit_Harington\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kit Harington\">Kit Harington</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liam_Cunningham\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Liam Cunningham\">Liam Cunningham</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carice_van_Houten\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Carice van Houten\">Carice Van Houten</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Turner\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sophie Turner\">Sophie Turner</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathalie_Emmanuel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nathalie Emmanuel\">Nathalie Emmanuel</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Missandei\" title=\"Missandei\">Missandei</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maisie_Williams\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Maisie Williams\">Maisie Williams</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conleth_Hill\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Conleth Hill\">Conleth Hill</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Pryce\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jonathan Pryce\">Jonathan Pryce</a> as the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Sparrow\" title=\"High Sparrow\">High Sparrow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristofer_Hivju\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kristofer Hivju\">Kristofer Hivju</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alfie_Allen\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Alfie Allen\">Alfie Allen</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Wlaschiha\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tom Wlaschiha\">Tom Wlaschiha</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Jaqen_H%27ghar\" title=\"Jaqen H&#39;ghar\">Jaqen H'ghar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iwan_Rheon\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Iwan Rheon\">Iwan Rheon</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_McElhatton\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Michael McElhatton\">Michael McElhatton</a> as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gwendoline_Christie\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Gwendoline Christie\">Gwendoline Christie</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dean-Charles_Chapman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dean-Charles Chapman\">Dean-Charles Chapman</a> as King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isaac_Hempstead_Wright\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Isaac Hempstead Wright\">Isaac Hempstead-Wright</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Co-starring\">Co-starring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Home&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Co-starring\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Max_von_Sydow\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Max von Sydow\">Max Von Sydow</a> as the <a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_raven\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Three-eyed raven\">three-eyed raven</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Malahide\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Patrick Malahide\">Patrick Malahide</a> as King <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Owen_Teale\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Owen Teale\">Owen Teale</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alliser_Thorne\" title=\"Alliser Thorne\">Alliser Thorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ben_Crompton\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ben Crompton\">Ben Crompton</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Eddison_Tollett\" title=\"Eddison Tollett\">Eddison Tollett</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pilou_Asb%C3%A6k\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Pilou Asbæk\">Pilou Asbæk</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Feast\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Michael Feast\">Michael Feast</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Aeron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Aeron Greyjoy\">Aeron Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacob_Anderson\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jacob Anderson\">Jacob Anderson</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Worm\" title=\"Grey Worm\">Grey Worm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gemma_Whelan\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Gemma Whelan\">Gemma Whelan</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Yara Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristian_Nairn\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kristian Nairn\">Kristian Nairn</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Hodor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Faye_Marsay\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Faye Marsay\">Faye Marsay</a> as the <a href=\"/index.php/Waif\" title=\"Waif\">waif</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellie_Kendrick\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ellie Kendrick\">Ellie Kendrick</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Portman\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Daniel Portman\">Daniel Portman</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Podrick_Payne\" title=\"Podrick Payne\">Podrick Payne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ian_Whyte_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ian Whyte (actor)\">Ian Whyte</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Wun_Weg_Wun_Dar_Wun\" title=\"Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun\">Wun Wun</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kae_Alexander\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kae Alexander\">Kae Alexander</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Leaf\" title=\"Leaf\">Leaf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haf%C3%BE%C3%B3r_J%C3%BAl%C3%ADus_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Hafþór Júlíus Björnsson\">Hafþór Júlíus Björnsson</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elizabeth_Webster\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Elizabeth Webster\">Elizabeth Webster</a> as Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Bolton</a></li>\n<li>Dylan Edwards as a King's Landing boaster</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Rycroft\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Richard Rycroft\">Richard Rycroft</a> as Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Wolkan\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wolkan\">Wolkan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=Paul_Rattray&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Paul Rattray (page does not exist)\">Paul Rattray</a> as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Harald_Karstark\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Harald Karstark\">Harald Karstark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brenock_O%27Connor\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Brenock O&#39;Connor\">Brenock O'Connor</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Olly\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Olly\">Olly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nell_Tiger_Free\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nell Tiger Free\">Nell Tiger Free</a> as Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Annette_Tierney\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Annette Tierney\">Annette Tierney</a> as young <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Nan\" title=\"Old Nan\">Nan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sam_Coleman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sam Coleman (page does not exist)\">Sam Coleman</a> as young <a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Wylis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fergus_Leathem&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Fergus Leathem (page does not exist)\">Fergus Leathem</a> as young <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a></li>\n<li>Richard Laing as a Lannister captain</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebastian_Croft\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sebastian Croft\">Sebastian Croft</a> as young <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cordelia_Hill\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cordelia Hill\">Cordelia Hill</a> as young <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=Matteo_Elezi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Matteo Elezi (page does not exist)\">Matteo Elezi</a> as young <a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen Stark</a></li>\n<li>Michael Hayes as a Night's Watchman</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Fortune\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Brian Fortune\">Brian Fortune</a> as First Builder <a href=\"/index.php/Othell_Yarwyck\" title=\"Othell Yarwyck\">Othell Yarwyck</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Condron\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Michael Condron\">Michael Condron</a> as First Steward <a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a></li>\n<li>Tony Flynn as Night's Watchman</li>\n<li>Robert Fawsitt as a loyal Night's Watchman</li>\n<li>Steve Cash as a loyal Night's Watchman</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-ed